---
// Component for the 4-step investment process
---

<section class="relative py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 via-white to-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        De datos a decisiones de inversión, <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[var(--color-azul-electrico)] to-[var(--color-verde-exito)] bg-clip-text text-transparent">en 4 pasos</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Process Steps -->
    <div class="relative lg:pl-24">
      <!-- Connector Line (hidden on mobile, visible on desktop) -->
      <div
        class="hidden lg:block absolute left-10 top-0 bottom-0 w-1 bg-gradient-to-b from-[var(--color-azul-electrico)] via-[var(--color-celeste-futuro)] to-[var(--color-verde-exito)] rounded-full"
      >
      </div>

      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="relative mb-12 lg:mb-20 group">
        <div
          class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-start lg:items-start gap-6 lg:gap-8"
        >
          <!-- Content -->
          <div class="flex-1 lg:pl-0">
            <div
              class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-2xl hover:border-[var(--color-azul-electrico)]/20 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:transform group-hover:-translate-y-1"
            >
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
                <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-azul-electrico)] to-[var(--color-celeste-futuro)] text-white text-sm font-bold">1</span>
                <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 flex-1">
                  Explorá el mercado completo
                </h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-azul-electrico)] mb-3 ml-12">
                Explorá todos los remates en el mapa
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-12">
                Accedé a todos los remates judiciales del país, organizados en un mapa interactivo. Ubicación, tipo de propiedad y estado general del proceso, todo en un solo lugar.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="relative mb-12 lg:mb-20 group">
        <div
          class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-start lg:items-start gap-6 lg:gap-8"
        >
          <!-- Content -->
          <div class="flex-1 lg:pl-0">
            <div
              class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-2xl hover:border-[var(--color-celeste-futuro)]/20 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:transform group-hover:-translate-y-1"
            >
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
                <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-celeste-futuro)] to-[var(--color-verde-exito)] text-white text-sm font-bold">2</span>
                <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 flex-1">
                  Estudio de Propiedad · Análisis legal inicial
                </h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-celeste-futuro)] mb-3 ml-12">
                Identificá riesgos antes de avanzar
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-12">
                Con nuestro Estudio de Propiedad, analizamos anotaciones, planos, información registral y riesgos legales clave para determinar si una propiedad es candidata real de inversión.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="relative mb-12 lg:mb-20 group">
        <div
          class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-start lg:items-start gap-6 lg:gap-8"
        >
          <!-- Content -->
          <div class="flex-1 lg:pl-0">
            <div
              class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-2xl hover:border-[var(--color-verde-exito)]/20 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:transform group-hover:-translate-y-1"
            >
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
                <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-verde-exito)] to-[var(--color-morado-inspiracion)] text-white text-sm font-bold">3</span>
                <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 flex-1">
                  Validación judicial
                </h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-verde-exito)] mb-3 ml-12">
                Confirmá que el remate es viable
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-12">
                Profundizamos el Estudio de Propiedad con la revisión del expediente judicial: confirmamos que el proceso esté activo, evaluamos su estado real y detectamos posibles bloqueos o contingencias.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4 -->
      <div class="relative mb-12 lg:mb-0 group">
        <div
          class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-start lg:items-start gap-6 lg:gap-8"
        >
          <!-- Content -->
          <div class="flex-1 lg:pl-0">
            <div
              class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-2xl hover:border-[var(--color-naranja-accion)]/20 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:transform group-hover:-translate-y-1"
            >
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
                <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-morado-inspiracion)] to-[var(--color-naranja-accion)] text-white text-sm font-bold">4</span>
                <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 flex-1">
                  Acompañamiento estratégico Subaxa
                </h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-naranja-accion)] mb-3 ml-12">
                Preparación y acompañamiento para ganar
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-12">
                Definimos la estrategia, validamos rentabilidad y te acompañamos profesionalmente hasta el día del remate para maximizar tus probabilidades de éxito.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Add smooth hover animation */
  .hover\:shadow-xl {
    transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease-in-out;
  }
  
  /* Ensure proper spacing on mobile */
  @media (max-width: 1023px) {
    .relative.mb-12 {
      padding-left: 0;
    }
  }

  /* Custom animations for the dots on the connector line */
  @keyframes pulse-slow {
    0%, 100% {
      opacity: 0.4;
      transform: translateX(-50%) scale(0.8);
    }
    50% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateX(-50%) scale(1.2);
    }
  }

  .animate-pulse-slow {
    animation: pulse-slow 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .animate-pulse-slow-delay {
    animation: pulse-slow 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    animation-delay: 1s;
  }

  .animate-pulse-slow-delay-2 {
    animation: pulse-slow 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    animation-delay: 2s;
  }

  /* Smooth gradient text animation */
  @keyframes gradient-shift {
    0%, 100% {
      background-position: 0% 50%;
    }
    50% {
      background-position: 100% 50%;
    }
  }

  .bg-clip-text {
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    background-size: 200% auto;
  }
</style>
